<bibRefCitation id="EFFA4B33871EAA01458DFDCBDF1EA877" author="Moure" box="[912,1150,568,595]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref21502" refString="Moure J. S., Melo G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo F. 2007. Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure J. S., Urban D. &amp; Melo G. A. R. (orgs) Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region: 83 - 142. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitibrazil." type="book chapter" year="2007">
